title: 8 October 2013, Heroic Guerrila Day, Che, Fidel, Cuba
description:
8 October 2013, Heroic Guerrila Day, Che, Fidel, Cuba

To honour the International Day of the Heroic Guerrila, Che Guevara, here is a modest collection of ebooks, mostly pdf but some epubs as well.

The collection includes everything which I have about Cuba, Che and Fidel, including 4 original scans; rest is collected from other posters at TPB, now defunct library.nu and still working Library Genesis.

Most of the books are either supportive of the revolution, or scholarly analysis, but some anti revolution books as well, though not the type Miami bigots.

All the books are in English.

The newest scan is: Che.Guevara.Talks.To.Young.People~Introduction.by.Mary-Alice.Waters.(2000,2005)
